        dc:description           "Figures 67 - 70. Trissolcus flavipes 67 female (USNMENT 00916409), head, mesosoma, metasoma, lateral view 68 female (USNMENT 00916409), head, mesosoma, metasoma, dorsal view 69 female lectotype (NHRS-HEVA 000002617), head, anterior view 70 female (holotype of T. circus) (ZMAS 0143), head, anterior view. Scale bars in millimeters." , "Figure 7 - 12. 7 T. mitsukurii, female (USNMENT 00675722), axillar crescent, lateral view 8 T. tumidus, female (USNMENT 00979425), axillar crescent, lateral view 9 T. flavipes, holotype of T. circus, female (ZMAS 0143), axillar crescent, lateral view 10 T. japonicus, female (USNMENT 00675989), axillar crescent, lateral view. 11 T. saakowi, female (USNMENT 00977544) axillar crescent, lateral view 12 T. nycteridaner, female (USNMENT 00896178), axillar crescent, lateral view. Scale bars in millimeters." ;
